Trademarks
================================================================

"FullSense" (umbrella brand and spec name), "llmesh", "llive", and "llove"
are trademarks of Kazufumi Furuse. See the per-product TRADEMARK.md files
(currently authoritative copy in `llive/TRADEMARK.md`) for the brand
hierarchy and trademark usage guidelines.

FullSense brand hierarchy:

    FullSense (umbrella) — brand + technical specification (v1.1)
      ├─ llmesh — secure LLM hub / on-prem MCP server
      ├─ llive  — self-evolving modular memory LLM framework
      └─ llove  — TUI dashboard / HITL workbench

A PyPI namespace migration to `fullsense-*` is planned for v1.0; see
`llive/docs/v1.0_migration_plan.md` for the rename plan and timeline.

================================================================
Third-party
================================================================

The portal uses the `just-the-docs` Jekyll remote theme
(https://github.com/just-the-docs/just-the-docs), MIT-licensed, and
Mermaid (https://github.com/mermaid-js/mermaid), MIT-licensed. Both are
loaded by GitHub Pages at render time and are not vendored in this
repository.

